subject: Add housekeeping module and staging cleaner

(1 comment)

Looks okay to me. I would tend to almost call this a feature more than a bug. It's clearly bad behavior, but it's not a regression in W and has never been a thing that was broken. But, I'll defer to the glance-stable-maint people on that :)
